{"title":"京都吟草","authors":["林林"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"京都吟草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京都建都１２００周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平城读罢忆平安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敕撰诗书耀艺坛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔海情深新景象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和风汉月庆同天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：公元７９４年，京都继奈良平城朝后建都为平安朝，当时天皇敕撰三部汉诗集，传播唐风的诗艺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十三间堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雕像庄严堂上立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈祥惟念众生安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手持法器灵威力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼怪焉能不胆寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：三十三间堂为日本国宝，正名是莲华王院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水寺楼秋望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩上危楼境界宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭栏一望鸟盘旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋阳淡淡无热力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艳艳丹枫似火燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岚山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船从山下樱丛过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡月桥长似卧波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴翳散开天皎亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨中诗句再吟哦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：雨中诗是岚山周恩来诗碑的诗作。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}